model.name: LV Formal Dimension Chelsea Boot
model.disambiguatingDescription: The LV Formal Dimension Chelsea boot draws inspiration from Louis Vuitton's Spring-Summer 2022 men's show. It contrasts a classic upper in smooth calf leather with a colorblock rubber outsole and a heel engraved with the LV Initials and Monogram Flowers to create an original 3D-print effect. This model's elastic side panels are subtly decorated with the Monogram pattern.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Black
  • Calf leather
  • Elastic side panels
  • Rubber outsole
  • Monogram Flowers and LV Initials on the heel
  • Monogram-canvas back loop
  • Made in Italy
